Popular singer, Harrysong, has revealed that his ex-girlfriend lied to get money from him about him having a set of twins. Recall that in 2017, Harrysong had announced the birth of twins with his ex-girlfriend in Beverly Hills, California, United States. The twins were named ‘Perez’, and ‘Tare’. However in a turn of events, Harrysong took to Instagram urging people to stop addressing him as father of twins. He disclosed that the ex-girlfriend took money from him and lied about having twins for him. On his Instagram page, Harrysong wrote “Addressing this issue, I’m not Baba twins or daddy ejima.That lady never gave birth she lied and was just eating my money. My first child is Daviva”. His revelation has since sparked a plethora of comments on social media.